            "title": "全日收市｜港股升249點本地股撐市  一周計恒指升科指跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股全日升249點，地產股揚升，滙控(00005)、友邦(10299)、新地(00016)為升市主力，內需股跑輸，一周計恒指升217點，惟科指及國指累跌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"滙控 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20190503_FI_AP_HSBC_source-ap_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"滙控 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20190503_FI_AP_HSBC_source-ap_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">滙控 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數全日報26630，升249點或0.95%，今早開升66點或0.25%，報26447，早段低見26375，跌6點或0.02%，為半日低位，其後反覆向上，午後升破上午高位，報26630，後段見26701，升320點或1.21%，為全日高位。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"滙控 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20190503_FI_AP_HSBC_source-ap_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"滙控 (AP圖片)\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20190503_FI_AP_HSBC_source-ap_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">滙控 (AP圖片)</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：新鴻基地產官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-180054_source-web_新地_新鴻基地產00016-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：新鴻基地產官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-180054_source-web_新地_新鴻基地產00016-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：新鴻基地產官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：藥明生物官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240723_FI_source-web_02269.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明生物官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240723_FI_source-web_02269.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：藥明生物官網影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：康師傅2024年度年報封面\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250423_FI_source-web_00322-2024.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：康師傅2024年度年報封面\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250423_FI_source-web_00322-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：康師傅2024年度年報封面</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"滙控 (AP圖片)\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20190503_FI_AP_HSBC_source-ap_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">滙控 (AP圖片)</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：新鴻基地產官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-180054_source-web_新地_新鴻基地產00016-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：新鴻基地產官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明生物官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240723_FI_source-web_02269.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：藥明生物官網影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：康師傅2024年度年報封面\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250423_FI_source-web_00322-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：康師傅2024年度年報封面</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數全日升28點或0.56%，報5137點，今早開升7點或0.15%，報5117。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生國企指數全日升45點或0.51%，報8859點，今早開升3點或0.04%，報8817點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交2884.2億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">全周計恒指升217點或0.82% ; 國指跌100點或1.12% ; 科指一周累跌74點或1.42%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指報26608，升241或0.91%，低水23點 ; 科指期貨升18點或0.35%，報5141，高水3點 ; 國指期貨報8879，升59點或0.67%，高水20點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">地產股有追捧，新地(00016)全日升7.41%，報146.4元，為表現最佳藍籌股，高盛升目標價至164元，花旗把目標價由105元升至168元。集團半年基礎溢利升16.7%至122.13億元，中期增至98仙。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">長實(01113)升3.58%，報49.78元 ; 恒隆地產(00101)升3.84%，報10.27元；恒基地產(00012)升2.9%，報35.44元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：新鴻基地產官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-180054_source-web_新地_新鴻基地產00016-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：新鴻基地產官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-180054_source-web_新地_新鴻基地產00016-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：新鴻基地產官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)及友邦(01299)撐市，滙控收升1.59%，推升恒指43點 ; 友邦升2.48%，報86.8元，共貢獻恒指78點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">生科醫藥股向好，藥明生物(02269)升5.06%，報40.22元 ; 再鼎醫藥(09688)虧損收窄，全日升4.01%，報15.06元 ; 石藥(01093)出售傳播平台業務，作價2.3億元人民幣，全日升3.77%報9.9元 ; 虧轉盈的百濟神州(06160)則跌1.08%，報192.3元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：藥明生物官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240723_FI_source-web_02269.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明生物官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240723_FI_source-web_02269.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：藥明生物官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內需股跑輸，康師傅(00322)跌1.06%，報13.09元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 美的集團(00300)跌1.36%，報90.85元 ; 萬洲(00288)跌1.21%，報9.84元 ; 恆安國際(01044)跌1.15%，報29.18元 ; 百威亞太保01876)跌1.39%，報7.79元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">百度(09888)上季經調整盈利跌42%，全日升0.24%，報123.7元。其他科網向好，支持大市，騰訊(00700)升1.17%，報518元；阿里巴巴(09988)跌0.07%，報142.9元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：康師傅2024年度年報封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250423_FI_source-web_00322-2024.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：康師傅2024年度年報封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250423_FI_source-web_00322-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：康師傅2024年度年報封面</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
